data.description: Welcome to Wildflower, Mesa del Sol! This elegantly updated pool home is outfitted with granite kitchen countertops, stainless steel appliances, modern  fixtures, and stylish/newer flooring. Tranquil backyard oasis boasts covered patio, pergola, & lush landscaping, with enough space for a hidden dog run. Pride of ownership shows here in this fantastically located Foothills home. This isn't going to last — schedule your showing before it's gone!
